[name]
Errors to POD source

[options]
errors pod

[input]
=over 4

=item Foo

Bar.

=head1 NEXT

[output]
.IP "Foo" 4
.IX Item "Foo"
Bar.
.SH "NEXT"
.IX Header "NEXT"
.SH "POD ERRORS"
.IX Header "POD ERRORS"
Hey! \fBThe above document had some coding errors, which are explained below:\fR
.IP "Around line 7:" 4
.IX Item "Around line 7:"
You forgot a '=back' before '=head1'
